HEADWORD: Teens
<hw>Teens</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Ten</er>.]</ety> <def>The years of one's age having the termination
<xex>-teen</xex>, beginning with thirteen and ending with nineteen;
<as>as, a girl in her <ex>teens</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

